snippet.title: Imagine Earth - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
In this build-up strategy game you build global colonies on distant planets. 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/280720

Establish space trade and research to lead your corporation into wealth and prosperity. Find allies, compete against rivals, and protect your civilization from natural disasters and climate change.
